    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small drinking glasses for spirits, generally of 2- or 3-ounce capacity, with a funnel or conical bowl and a short rudimentary stem resting on a heavy foot.</Note_Text>
